{"tid":1101384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過去3年117正規警員被捕　休班警佔逾七成","createTime":"2019-04-11T04:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T09:22:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b101870c4c2e88f5cbfb3b481e4123cd08cdeb7d","tid":1101384,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190410/s00001/4bea68e3ecbe2f0ca9b1109db8cb727d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190410%2Fs00001%2F4bea68e3ecbe2f0ca9b1109db8cb727d.jpg&h=62fccdac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年警員犯罪情況備受關注。警務處回覆立法會特別財委會的數據顯示，過去3年共117名正規警員被捕，其中90人被警方拘捕，其餘27人被其他執法部門如廉政公署及海關拘捕。過去3年被捕警員當中，87人在休班期間涉案被捕，即休班警佔逾七成。<br />\n<br />\n警務處數據顯示，2016年至2018年每年被警務處拘捕的正規警員分別有34、18及38人，當中分別有21、15及30人涉嫌干犯警隊定義為罪行性質屬較嚴重的刑事案件，牽涉強姦、非禮、傷人及嚴重毆打、刑事恐嚇、盜竊、詐騙等罪行。據警方了解，過去3年每年分別另有9、11及7名正規警員被廉政公署及海關等其他執法部門拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n另外，過去3年每年分別有33、23及31名正規警員在休班期間涉案被捕，合共87人，佔過去3年總數約74.4%。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警務處指出，警隊非常重視警員的誠信管理，前年2月成立「誠信管理特別工作小組」，檢視誠信管理制度及提出優化措施，去年5月推出「不恰當行為的徵兆及適時介入的指引」，協助管理層及各級人員適時介入同事與警隊價值觀不符的行為。</span>工作小組會繼續檢視及改善警隊的誠信管理制度，鞏固警隊在誠信、公正等方面的核心價值觀，維持市民對警員執行職務的信心與信任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190410/s00001/1554905559110/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB3%E5%B9%B4117%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E4%BD%94%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%83%E6%88%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190410%2Fs00001%2F1554905559110%2F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258E%25BB3%25E5%25B9%25B4117%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%25A6%258F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2588%2590&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=79f9005f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190410%2Fs00001%2F1554905559110%2F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258E%25BB3%25E5%25B9%25B4117%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%25A6%258F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2588%2590&h=d1b97c11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190410/s00001/1554905559110/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB3%E5%B9%B4117%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E4%BD%94%E9%80%BE%E4%B8%83%E6%88%90</a>"},{"pid":"f30094d9c6dc342a94edff4a8d06a92bc2eb9391","tid":1101384,"uid":77985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:07:11.000Z","msg":"你地無做錯到"},{"pid":"284332aa4b0f27440e05b1c034233ffb35e21b64","tid":1101384,"uid":205844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"痴線，警察犯案仲多過d賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5909ce5098c068e225946eb48d22bde671199d25","tid":1101384,"uid":106633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:22:42.000Z","msg":"痴線三成人返緊工都犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}